<div class="contactUs row">
  <div class="contactUs__greenBox col-xs-12 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-4">
    <div class="text-uppercase">Contact Us <span class="contactUs__andSign">&</span></div>
    <div>Let us pour your next drink!</div>
    <div>Serving Wichita and Kansas areas</div>
    <form class="contactUs__submitForm">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="submitForm__name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sumbmitForm__name" placeholder="Enter Name">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="submitForm__company">Company</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sumbmitForm__company" placeholder="Enter Company">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="submitForm__phone">Phone</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sumbmitForm__phone" placeholder="Enter Phone">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="submitForm__email">Email address</label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="submitForm__email" placeholder="Enter Email">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <p class="help-block">
          Breifly describe :<br>
          - What type of services are you looking for?<br>
          - What is the setting?<br>
          - How did you hear about Xclusive?<br>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <img src="/images/telephone.png">
    <div>Need more info? No problem!</div>
    <div>Give us a call at 316.555.5555</div>
  </div>
  <div class="contactUs__socialBar col-xs-12">
    <p>Connect with us for the latest photos, events, and decor!</p>
  </div>
</div>
